&quot;Because, I am a Decepticon,&quot; her deep growl feline femme voice stated, as 
sher slipped her hand under & quickly got up to face her &#39;guests&#39;. 

Her optics glanced to the 2. Then noticed Wheeljack & his insignia, as her 
optic grew larger with a stunned recognition. &quot;Autobot Wheeljack!&quot; she 
hissed.  

This was NOT how she wished for it all to go. Again, she cursed Alpha Trion 
for reviving her like this. 






